OL,3,CPre-trial hearing set for inmate
OL,4,Ccharged with murdering child-killer
OL,5,CIan Huntley
OL,7,FAn inmate has appeared before a crown
OL,8,Fcourt judge after he was charged with
OL,9,Fthe prison murder of child-killer Ian
OL,10,FHuntley.
OL,12,FAnthony Russell, 43, appeared at
OL,13,FTeesside Crown Court via videolink
OL,14,Ffrom HMP Frankland, near Durham, for a
OL,15,F10-minute preliminary hearing on
OL,16,FThursday 12 March.
OL,18,FRussell, who is from Coventry, is
OL,19,Fcharged with a single offence of
OL,20,Fmurdering the 52-year-old on 26
OL,21,FFebruary.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773411080
OL,3,CPre-trial hearing set for inmate
OL,4,Ccharged with murdering child-killer
OL,5,CIan Huntley
OL,7,FHe was not asked to enter a plea and
OL,8,Fwas told there will be a pre-trial
OL,9,Fpreparation hearing on 24 April at
OL,10,FNewcastle Crown Court.
OL,12,FThe judge confirmed with Tyrone Smith
OL,13,FKC, defending, that Russell was on the
OL,14,Flink and cooperating fully with the
OL,15,Fproceedings.
OL,17,FConcluding the hearing, Judge Laird
OL,18,Fsaid: "Mr Russell, that is the end of
OL,19,Fthe case today.
OL,26,@zD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
