OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773411080
OL,3,CPre-trial hearing set for inmate
OL,4,Ccharged with murdering child-killer
OL,5,CIan Huntley
OL,7,F"You will next be before the court on
OL,8,FApril 24 and I direct you may attend
OL,9,Fthat hearing remotely.
OL,11,F"If your lawyers feel there is merit
OL,12,Fin you being at Newcastle Crown Court
OL,13,Fthen they will be at liberty to apply
OL,14,Fto the court administratively to
OL,15,Fensure your attendance at that
OL,16,Fhearing."
OL,18,FRussell replied: "Thank you."
