PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773411080
OL,3,CPre-trial hearing set for inmate
OL,4,Ccharged with murdering child-killer
OL,5,CIan Huntley
OL,7,FHuntley was reportedly attacked with a
OL,8,Fmetal bar in a workshop at HMP
OL,9,FFrankland near Durham, on 26 February.
OL,11,FThe 52-year-old was taken to the Royal
OL,12,FVictoria Infirmary, in Newcastle,
OL,13,Ffollowing the incident. He was
OL,14,Fconfirmed dead on Saturday 7 March.
OL,16,FThe ex-school caretaker was serving a
OL,17,Flife sentence at the maximum security
OL,18,Fjail for the 2002 murders of 10-year-
OL,19,Folds Holly Wells and Jessica Chapman.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
