FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773411080
OL,3,CPre-trial hearing set for inmate
OL,4,Ccharged with murdering child-killer
OL,5,CIan Huntley
OL,7,FHuntley, who was originally from
OL,8,FGrimsby, had served 23 years of his
OL,9,Fsentenced having been jailed in 2003.
OL,10,FAt the time he was told he would spend
OL,11,Fat least 40 years behind bars.
OL,13,FHe was found guilty of murdering Soham
OL,14,Fschoolgirls Holly and Jessica after
OL,15,Fthey left a barbecue to buy some
OL,16,Fsweets in August 2002.
OL,18,FHuntley was known to the girls because
OL,19,Fhe lived with Maxine Carr, a teaching
OL,20,Fassistant at their primary school.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
