CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1773411080
OL,3,CPre-trial hearing set for inmate
OL,4,Ccharged with murdering child-killer
OL,5,CIan Huntley
OL,7,FFollowing his conviction, an inquiry
OL,8,Fled by Lord Michael Bichard found
OL,9,Fserious flaws in the way potential
OL,10,Femployees were vetted to work with
OL,11,Fchildren and vulnerable people.
OL,13,FThe review brought about major changes
OL,14,Fin the vetting and barring system, and
OL,15,Fled to the creation of a national
OL,16,Fintelligence database which enabled
OL,17,Fpolice to share information about
OL,18,Fsuspects.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
